This partitioned dataset contains the following members:

$RECEIVE - issue 'hlq.SLM.PDS($RECEIVE)' to create usable
           asm, exec, load, msgs, and panels datasets
ASM      - assembler source
CHANGES  - change history for this application
EXEC     - tso transmit format rexx exec
LICENSE  - GNU Public License under which this package is made
           available
LOAD     - tso transmit format load library (with SLMREXXF module)
MSGS     - tso transmit format ispf msgs
PANELS   - tso transmit format ispf panels

Dependencies: OS/390 Version 2 Release 10 or above.

To test this application you can use the sample rexx exec in the exec
library called TESTSLM to allocate the appropriate libraries and
invoke the application.

NOTE: that local customizations are made in the SLMCUST rexx exec.

Updates are posted at my web site at http://www.lbdsoftware.com

Mutual support, questions, suggestions, etc. is supported at:

